public interface ListIterator
extends Iterator

interface ListIterator expands upon the functionality of Iterator by providing for bidirectional traversals Written by Roger West, University of Illinois at Springfield Adapted from code written by Mark Weiss in Data Structures and Problem Solving Using Java, 2nd edition, 2002
